channel.title: How to add empty, black tiles?
channel.description: You know if you teleport to a place that doesn't exist. (::tele 0000 0000) You are in a black oblivion, and you can't walk? How do I add those objects as parimeters? Around Lumbridge Castle for example.

Get a cache/map editor and delete everything around the castle
